Issue #11966: Injection Jakarta EE 9 FAT

Initial fat for testing injection with Jakarta EE 9. Repeat the following:
- EnvEntryTest
- RepeatableEnvEntryTest

timeline.bodyText: For future reference: last week I reviewed something for Andy that should fix the case mattering in the feature name for the repeatTest stuff.

replies.bodyText: :-) Yes, it was Andy that helped me figure out why it wasn't working.  He said he would get it fixed, but I thought it best going forward to just fix it.
